name: Curio Cards x Metakey 5th Year Anniversary

metadata.name: Curio Cards x Metakey (5th Year Anniversary)
metadata.description:
Inspired by MetaKey's Ganymede universe, Curio Cards thanks Metakey for their support of their 5th Year anniversary party that occurred on May 9th, 2022. 

MetaKey helped organize the live event at their headquarters located in Decentraland, making it a memorable experience for the attendees. As a thank you, Curio DAO gifted the Future card, along with accompanying artwork to give toast to an optimistic future. Sincerely, Curio DAO

Artwork by Wiv (https://twitter.com/wiv_ian)  
Music by Noxis (https://twitter.com/Aegiuscreator)
